Package: bib2acad
Type: Package
Title: Convert Bibtex to Markdown for the Hugo Academic Theme
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Peter Baumgartner <petzi53@gmail.com> [aut, cre]", 
    "Lorenzo Busetto <lbusett@gmail.com> [ctb]"
  ))
Description: Convert records of a Bibtex file (.bib) to separate .md files
    for the publications folder of the Hugo Academic Theme. Store optionally
    each record as a separate .bib file for the '/static/files/citations' 
    folder.
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Date: 2018-08-04
Contact: Peter Baumgartner <petzi53@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/petzi53/bib2acad
BugReports: http://github.com/petzi53/bib2acad/issues
